name: megadepth

owner.description: Bioconda is a distribution of bioinformatics software realized as a channel for the versatile Conda package manager.
owner.name: bioconda

summary: Megadepth is an efficient tool for extracting coverage related information from RNA and DNA-seq BAM and BigWig files. It supports reading whole-genome coverage from BAM files and writing either indexed TSV or BigWig files, as well as efficient region coverage summary over intervals from both types of files.
